<p><sup><a name="fn25" href="#fnB25">[23]</a></sup> 	Evidence to Senate Rural
and Regional Affairs and Transport Committee, Parliament of Australia, Canberra,
15 February 2006, 4 (Jim
Varghese, Director-General, Queensland Department of
