2001</a></i> (Qld) <a href="http://www.austlii.edu.au/au/legis/qld/consol_act/acapa2001229/s18.html" class="autolink_findacts">s 18(2)</a>; <i>Prevention of Cruelty to Animals Act 1985</i> (SA) s
